    "pretraining": {
        "value": "Stage 1: Visual-enhanced perception (ViT and CNN frozen, extract multi-layer and multi-scale features); Stage 2: Cross-modal mutual comprehension (unfrozen self-attention and RMSNorm in LLaMA-2, trained on LAION-400M and COCO Caption for vision-language alignment); Stage 3: Unified instruction tuning for RS (bias tuning of linear layers in LLaMA-2, trained on MMRS-1M for multi-task RS instruction following)",
